c: 14
v: 9
t: "Have you not heard the tales of those gone by __ the people of Nooh, Aads, Samoods, and others after them? Now, no one knows them except Allah. The messengers brought them clear proofs! But they shoved their hands in the messengers´ mouths, _ (forbade them to speak) _ and said, \"Here! We reject what you were sent with. We are reluctant and skeptical about your message"